cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the robustness of deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper proposes a method for enhancing robustness by decomposing a multiclass model into binary models, which is a technique that is commonly used in neural networks (cs.NE).
